00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:19,320
That's about 7% of the Roman Senate.

333
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,460
That's a lot of people, man.

334
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,360
Right? 7% of the Roman Senate.

335
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:30,460
