410
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:56,340
hurt the interests of the senators

411
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:57,940
and nobility in the short term.

412
00:23:58,100 --> 00:23:59,980
This is what caused the conflict. Okay?

413
00:24:05,460 --> 00:24:08,440
And because Caesar was

