00:27:12,280 --> 00:27:16,100
Because being king was the
ultimate taboo in Rome.

466
00:27:17,080 --> 00:27:21,660
Does that make sense? Julius
Caesar could not imagine

467
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:25,020
