mean the death of the Republic.

482
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:17,440
And that's not taboo.

483
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:19,680
That's a rubicon he refused to cross.

484
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:24,600
Okay? So we can imagine that Caesar
