00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:34,360
He would make the necessary reforms.

489
00:28:34,540 --> 00:28:37,800
And then he would retire and
lead the Republic as it was.

490
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:41,860
Okay? Okay.

